fields.name: Banana
fields.description: A yellow fruit usually grown in tropical climates.

fields.name: Apple
fields.description: The apple tree is a deciduous ree in the rose family best known for its sweet, pomaceous fruit, the apple.  It is cultivated worldwide as a fruit tree, and is the most widely grown species in the genus Malus.

fields.name: Broccoli
fields.description: An edible green plant in the cabbage family whose large flower-head is eaten as a vegetable.
